column2:
probit1<-glm(union_vote == "For the union" ~
                  male*tenure_num + as.factor(Q6.3) + rk_age,
                family = binomial(link="probit"),
                data = thd)


probit2<-glm(union_vote == "For the union" ~
                  male*tenure_num + nonwhite + rk_age + male,
                family = binomial(link="probit"),
                data = thd)

stargazer::stargazer(ols, probit1, probit2)
as.factor(Q6.3)Hispanic or Latino/Latina,Asian or Pacific Islander
as.factor(Q6.3)Hispanic or Latino/Latina,Black or African American
as.factor(Q6.3)White,Hispanic or Latino/Latina,American Indian or Alaskan native
